OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FThe Government is confident the
OL,7,FHillsborough Law will clear its
OL,8,Fremaining stages in the House of
OL,9,FCommons before MPs leave for the
OL,10,Fsummer.
OL,12,FMinister previously suggested the law
OL,13,Fchange would not be passed before the
OL,14,Fsummer recess due to concerns it would
OL,15,Fnot apply to members of the security
OL,16,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
