PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FThe Public Office (Accountability)
OL,7,FBill would create a legally-
OL,8,Fenforceable duty of candour which
OL,9,Fcompels public officials and
OL,10,Fauthorities to act transparently when
OL,11,Finvestigations and inquiries take
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,FIt takes its name from the
OL,15,FHillsborough disaster in 1989 when 97
OL,16,FLiverpool fans were killed at the
OL,17,Ffootball stadium in Sheffield in a
OL,18,Fcrush during an FA Cup semi-final
OL,19,Fmatch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FAfter the disaster, key public
OL,7,Fservants, including the police, were
OL,8,Ffound to have not told the truth about
OL,9,Fthe decisions taken leading up to the
OL,10,Ffatal crush at the Leppings Lane end
OL,11,Fof the ground.
OL,13,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy said
OL,14,Fhe was "confident" the draft
OL,15,Flegislation would be back "in the
OL,16,Fcoming days" at the despatch box last
OL,17,Fweek, but other Government figures
OL,18,Fsuggested it would not return until
OL,19,Fafter the summer recess.
OL,26,@vD@HOUvD@RO]wD@[OUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FBoth Sir Keir Starmer and his likely
OL,7,Fsuccessor Andy Burnham have expressed
OL,8,Fsupport for the law change, but it had
OL,9,Fbeen repeatedly delayed over concerns
OL,10,Ffrom the security services about how
OL,11,Fit could impact spies.
OL,13,FThe Government now believes it has
OL,14,Freached a point where individual
OL,15,Femployees and ex-employees of the
OL,16,Fintelligence services will be covered
OL,17,Fby a duty of candour, without
OL,18,Fcompromising national security.
OL,20,FThis will be set out in amendments to
OL,21,Fthe Bill, due to be debated this week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FA Government source said: "This is an
OL,7,Foverwhelming victory after months of
OL,8,Fhard work to find a solution that
OL,9,Fensures we have a duty of candour that
OL,10,Fapplies to the intelligence services
OL,11,Fwithout compromising national security.
OL,13,F"The Hillsborough Law will
OL,14,Ffundamentally change the balance of
OL,15,Fpower so the state can never hide from
OL,16,Fthe people it is supposed to serve,
OL,17,Fand so victims can always get justice."
OL,26,@nD@[OUuD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FThe latest amendments to the Bill
OL,7,Fcreate a process where intelligence
OL,8,Femployees send information under the
OL,9,Fduty of candour to the head of their
OL,10,Forganisation, who would then be
OL,11,Fresponsible for passing it on to
OL,12,Fpublic investigators.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough Law Now campaign,
OL,7,Fwhich has been campaigning for the law
OL,8,Fchange, welcomed news that the Bill
OL,9,Fwill return to the Commons, and
OL,10,Fdescribed it as "a major step towards
OL,11,Fdelivering the landmark changes that
OL,12,Fbereaved families and survivors have
OL,13,Ffought for over decades to prevent
OL,14,Fstate cover-ups".
OL,16,FThe campaign added: "The Government
OL,17,Fhas now conceded that there will be no
OL,18,Fcarve-outs, no exemptions for security
OL,19,Fservices or anyone else, breaking the
OL,20,Fimpasse that has persisted since
OL,21,FJanuary.
OL,26,@rD@QOUvD@PO]xD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,F"This is an important milestone, not
OL,7,Fjust for Hillsborough families, but
OL,8,Ffor every family who has experienced a
OL,9,Fcover-up and lack of accountability
OL,10,Ffrom public authorities. We are a big
OL,11,Fstep closer to ensuring that no family
OL,12,Fhas to again fight for the truth for
OL,13,Fdecades.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783939847
OL,3,CHillsborough Law to return to Commons
OL,4,Cbefore summer recess
OL,6,F"Once the Bill completes its Commons
OL,7,Fstages this week, the journey
OL,8,Fcontinues in the House of Lords. We
OL,9,Fwill keep working with peers,
OL,10,Fparliamentarians and families to
OL,11,Fensure this legislation reaches the
OL,12,Fstatute book and delivers the change
OL,13,Fthat has been promised for so long."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
